{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"@property","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"text":"nonatomic","kind":"keyword"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"assign","kind":"keyword"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"BOOL","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"showsUserLocation","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Setting this property to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"YES"},{"type":"text","text":" causes the map view to use the Core Location"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"framework to find the current location. As long as this property is "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"YES"},{"type":"text","text":", the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"map view continues to track the user’s location and update it periodically."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This property does not indicate whether the user’s position is actually visible"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"on the map, only whether the map view is allowed to display it. To determine"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"whether the user’s position is visible, use the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"userLocationVisible"},{"type":"text","text":" property."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The default value of this property is "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NO"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Your app must specify a value for ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NSLocationWhenInUseUsageDescription"},{"text":" or","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NSLocationAlwaysUsageDescription"},{"text":" in its ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Info.plist"},{"text":" to satisfy the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"requirements of the underlying Core Location framework when enabling this","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"property.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If you implement a custom location manager, set the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"locationManager"},{"text":" before","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"calling ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"showsUserLocation"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]}]}],"metadata":{"title":"showsUserLocation","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"fragments":[{"text":"showsUserLocation","kind":"identifier"}],"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(py)showsUserLocation","symbolKind":"property","roleHeading":"Instance Property","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"showsUserLocation"}],"role":"symbol","remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapView.h#L590","fileName":"MLNMapView.h"}},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/showsUserLocation","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"]]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A Boolean value indicating whether the map may display the user location."}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/showsuserlocation"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"kind":"symbol","references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView/showsUserLocation":{"type":"topic","title":"showsUserLocation","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/showsuserlocation","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"showsUserLocation","kind":"ide